metadata.name: Searching
metadata.description:
"Searching" is the second of five images in a photographic series entitled "WET: Chapter 1" by Lindsey Byrnes.

In this series the artist takes you on an underwater journey. Documenting her search for love and security; swimming through the waters whilst subconsciously remembering being in utero.

This photograph has been minted to the Ethereum blockchain as a limited edition ERC-1155 token. Copyright is retained by Lindsey Byrnes.
